{"tid":1716053,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"取消快活谷夜馬 更勝裝修美心千回","createTime":"2019-11-13T08:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T09:04:50.000Z","uid":61242,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cc2dd21d2beda1e268572313348055633a620618","tid":1716053,"uid":61242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:47:41.000Z","msg":"講開黃藍經濟圈，其實大家裝修都出晒力，但其實馬會出名係藍絲竇，咩達官貴人政圈明星，唔係有隻馬就有會藉，經常入去宴會請朋友坐包廂拉頭馬喺度鳩威。<br />\n<br />\n一場賽馬，千萬億萬投注額，養隻馬又要馬房又要打種又要訓練又要谷獎金，背後駛幾多錢，一晚營業額雞碎咁多，停一場馬，班廢老冇得賭，啲政商界白白燒銀紙，大家仲記唔記得何妖都有馬架？<br />\n<br />\n雖然我知有巴打係玩開馬仔，國難當前賭其他嘢啦<br />\n<br />\n你唔俾我哋五十年不變，點解要俾你班名流馬照跑舞照跳？<br />\n<br />\n取消快活谷夜馬<br />\n更勝裝修美心千回<br />\n<br />\nYou burn us<br />\nYou burn with us"},{"pid":"d18c3cdd0710696d98ff7c44874ff4a168c31d14","tid":1716053,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:48:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1fd7479316a0c59dbbecf13317a20d8761dccd3f","tid":1716053,"uid":259329,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:49:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a93a1eefcee42fdad9519a4220a28565bd10886a","tid":1716053,"uid":61242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:49:09.000Z","msg":"自推一嘢"},{"pid":"a2e9fcc0c63b295933589851d1c18df0660af774","tid":1716053,"uid":61242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fd7479316a0c59dbbecf13317a20d8761dccd3f","tid":1716053,"uid":259329,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:49:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:49:55.000Z","msg":"冇馬跑，馬會都要營運，分分鐘開多幾次六合彩"},{"pid":"c78f8dcf3f7bc29d570a0ca862a36086fccd00b1","tid":1716053,"uid":61242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:53:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71b25f12eb490b60a0da742fb08a8f0234a5599d","tid":1716053,"uid":61242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:53:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5285c749b2ffc2f027b7ef4b16c96450f3f409a8",